      credits_h1: 'Credits & Acknowledgments',
      credits_subtitle: 'We are grateful to these organizations for making Readmigo possible.',
      credits_sources_h2: 'Content Sources',
      credits_sources_p1: 'All books in Readmigo are sourced from public domain collections. We extend our heartfelt thanks to:',
      credits_standard_p: 'Standard Ebooks is a volunteer-driven project that produces new editions of public domain ebooks that are lovingly formatted, open source, free of U.S. copyright restrictions, and free of cost. Their dedication to quality typography, careful proofreading, and beautiful formatting makes classic literature accessible to everyone.',
      credits_gutenberg_p: 'Project Gutenberg is a library of over 70,000 free eBooks. They were the first provider of free electronic books, and have been digitizing and archiving cultural works since 1971. Their pioneering work has made countless classic works freely available to readers worldwide.',
      credits_commitment_h2: 'Our Commitment',
      credits_free_h3: 'Free Reading for Everyone',
      credits_free_p: 'All book content in Readmigo is completely free to read. We believe that classic literature should be accessible to everyone, regardless of their financial situation. This commitment honors the spirit of the public domain and the organizations that preserve these works.',
      credits_giving_h3: 'Giving Back',
      credits_giving_p: 'If we introduce paid services in the future (such as premium AI features), we commit to donating at least 10% of our revenue (subject to operational costs) to the content sources that make our service possible. This is our way of supporting the continued preservation and digitization of public domain works.',
      credits_oss_h2: 'Open Source Community',
      credits_oss_p: 'Readmigo is built with the help of many open source libraries and tools. We are thankful to the countless developers who contribute to the open source ecosystem, making it possible for projects like ours to exist.',
      credits_users_h2: 'Our Users',
      credits_users_p: 'Finally, we thank our users — readers, learners, and literature enthusiasts — for choosing Readmigo as your reading companion. Your feedback and support drive us to continuously improve.',
      credits_contact_p: 'Have questions or suggestions? Contact us at',
